What is TermTA

* TermTA is an on-line terminal program designed specifically for use in
  playing TeleArena, the popular BBS door game.
* TermTA is an interface composed of graphics and sound.

The advantage of using TermTA is that it is custom designed just for
playing the game. Thus you have a lot of features that your normal
term program like Telemate or QModem can't offer.

To help make learning TermTA as easy as possible, I've broken the docs
into these files...

